\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
If the wave speed is a non-constant function of 
\begin_inset Formula $u$
\end_inset

, then IVP 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand eqref
reference "prob:LinearWaveEquationWithSmoothIC"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

